<br>
::Pluto was dressed as a Roman centurion, his cape however was a midnight blue and so was the brush on top of his helmet::<br>
<br>
::Hades spoke up:: &quot;You wasted no time in coming here.&quot;<br>
<br>
::Pluto, having the same shadowy eyes from his helmet merely smirked and said:: &quot;What can I say, the rest of them took the high road, I took the low road.&quot;<br>
<br>
::Hades eyes narrowed as he walked over to a small table beside his throne.  He threw his hood back, and removed his crown and placed it upon there.  He then took the helmet that was on there and put it on his head.  Instantaneously he was wearing a Spartan's war outfit.  His sceptor had turned into a silver tipped fighting spear as he picked up a shield from the wall::  <br>
<br>
::Pluto smirked as he banged his shield and sword together ready for a fight:: &quot;I'm gonna rip you limb from limb&quot;...<br>
<br>
<br>
